      <div class="model-card"><h3>Ultra-2 dual-bowl</h3><p>Dual-flavor 2-bowl configuration, most common LA install. C-stores, juice bars, operators wanting two flavor options in one cabinet. Service spans both bowls + shared compressor.</p></div>
